data.description: Stunning waterfront home with pool, dock, and Wando river access in exclusive Park Island. Catch redfish from the short 150' dock with 13k pound boat lift. Three story custom build with 3-stop elevator, 3 car garage and 850 sqft ground floor guest suite. Master on the main level with spa bath and 2 walk in closets. Three guest rooms and a flex space with balcony on the 3rd floor. Salt water pool overlooking the marsh. Fully fenced turf yard. Gourmet kitchen with Thermador refrigerator and marble countertops. Dining room opens onto screened porch. Living room has coffered ceiling, built ins, gas fireplace and opens onto large deck overlooking pool. Study with pocket doors off the foyer. 3 bay garage has sealed floors, storage closet, and extra storage below front porch.
